{"tid":1557168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百英國議員籲英聯邦國家給香港居民第二公民身份","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:17:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63e767c23e0850a46d41772dc47a91f08674e200","tid":1557168,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"近130名英國國會議員，包括前港督彭定康，向外相藍韜文發表聯署信，呼籲英聯邦國家給予香港居民第二公民身份及居留權。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信說，中國最近的言論及行動，表明北京領導層已經脫離基本法規定，對維護香港生活方式的承諾，英聯邦國家應該為香港人提供保障，又要求將有關討論，列入明年在盧旺達舉行的英聯邦政府領導人會議議程。<br />\n<br />\n目前很多香港居民都持有BNO護照，但不享有英國居留權，藍韜文日前表明，若果更改規定，可能會破壞一國兩制。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479727-20190910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479727-20190910.htm&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDyWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=700194c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479727-20190910.htm&h=3ecb5c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479727-20190910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bbd5ce3c5c5ae7a19504d890c75ed14d6cdc16f7","tid":1557168,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"美聯邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1e2ed412c66a9641c221b027b63153c9628785","tid":1557168,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd5ce3c5c5ae7a19504d890c75ed14d6cdc16f7","tid":1557168,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"美聯邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"英"},{"pid":"cb55bfd9c1fef62079801709265eee23872d4425","tid":1557168,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c1e2ed412c66a9641c221b027b63153c9628785","tid":1557168,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,